fields.name: Men's Fanatics Orange Anaheim Ducks Home Breakaway Jersey
fields.description: This Anaheim Ducks Home Breakaway Jersey is a spirited piece to have for game day. Distinct graphics match those worn by players on the ice, making you feel like a member of your favourite team. The Fanatics fabric technology will keep you comfortable while cheering the Anaheim Ducks to victory.

fields.name: Men's Fanatics Heather Charcoal Anaheim Ducks Primary Logo Fleece Pullover Hoodie
fields.description: Your Anaheim Ducks wardrobe will be a whole lot mightier with this Primary Logo Fleece Pullover Hoodie. This Fanatics gear is made of a cotton-polyester blend to keep you feeling your best. The fresh graphics will make this your favorite piece of Ducks' gear.

fields.name: Carolina Panthers Nike Performance Fleece Pullover Hoodie - Mens
fields.description: Enjoy watching your team in comfort. Team branded, the hoodie offers a warm and cosy feel, and is perfect for gameday and everyday wear.
